item.description:
http://www.canadianamericanclub.com/Calendar-of-Events.html

Oct 19,20,21 2012 75th Diamond Jubilee Celebration at the Canadian American Club. Contact the club to get your tickets. Limited number of tickets available.So send in your check for 35.00 each to hold your ticket for you. It is first checks recieved will hold your ticket.

Oct 19 Friday- A Night of Music ---FREE Starts at 8:00pm Come listen to some members and special guests play some Maritime Music. Dance and enjoy some great food.
Oct 20 SaturdayDinner Dance with Irish Showband The Jackie Brown Band Dinner and Dance . There will be a catered buffet chicken dinner with all the trimmings and dessert. Great music and several special guests who will have some great stories about the last 75 years. Cocktail hour with appetizers downstairs 5:30-6:30pm before the dinner.(included in the price of the dinner) Dinner upstairs will be served at 6:30pm Dancing after the dinner.
Oct 21 Sunday Family Kitchen Party with Troy MacGillivray and friends.Admission is $15.00 each with children under 14 free with a adult. Troy will be teaching a fiddle workshop at noontime on Sunday.before the kitchen party. Contact Troy on his website for more information. WWW.troymacgillivray.com
